 <p>
  ABBREVIATE:
  <br/>
  The hands move in from the sides (not the front).
  <br/>
  <img border="0" height="317" src="images/abbreviate-13.jpg" width="337"/>
  <img border="0" height="317" src="images/abbreviate-14.jpg" width="337"/>
  <img border="0" height="317" src="images/abbreviate-15.jpg" width="337"/>
 </p>
 <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
  <hr align="left" color="#000000" size="1" width="50%"/>
  <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
   Notes:
   <br/>
   This is not the same sign as "get." The sign GET starts away from 
			the body and moves closer to the body.  The sign ABBREVIATE 
			starts with the hands a bit to the side and they move in toward the 
			center as they change into "S" hands.
   <br/>
   <br/>
